summary: For you guys who would like a preset to base a character on. Works for males too.
descriptionHtml:
I have 8 almost random and immersive CME presets in this .rar and they all sort of look like these images. I'm uploading this as a preset for people who would like to use them, I figure it's a good lore friendly base as I've made dozens of 'new' characters of Skyrim out of subtle slider and hair adjustments.

Mods used:
ECE and hair mods you can find here someplace. I have all of the hair mods installed and so should you.
http://www.tesgeneral.com/
I really liked the optional Lovergirl face texture but it seems it's been deleted from the Nexus so good luck finding it. She looks okay with default ECE textures though.

I hope you can get good at waifu creation with this file. Good luck and I hope you upload images if you make something out of it.

To install put the files in "C:Users___DocumentsMy GamesSkyrimCME_save" folder and then you can load them as presets in ECE's showracemenu. I use ygnord race.
author: The Official Waifu Rater
